author: rhuijben
msg: Reorder the arguments of libsvn_wc/status.c get_dir_status() to make a bit
more sense. Document the DIRENT argument. And remove some of the dirent
retrievals I added in r980153, as in these cases the value is unused anyway.
(get_dir_status): Reorder arguments and document DIRENT argument.
(make_dir_baton): Update caller. Skip retrieving dirent as it is not
used anyway. Pass cancel function and baton.
(handle_statii): Update caller.  Skip retrieving dirents as they are
used anyway. Pass cancel function and baton.
